    "bbox": [
      58.32,
      486.64,
      534.05,
      544.51
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, North-western, Southern and Uva provinces and in Anuradhapura, Mannar, Kandy, Nuwara-Eliya, Ampara and Batticaloa districts after 2.00 p.m.",
